"   Autocommands -------------------------------------------{{{

augroup vimrc_autocomands
  autocmd!
"     VimEnter Autocommands Group -----------------------------------------{{{

  " clear jump list
  autocmd VimEnter * silent clearjump

  " check vim dependencies before opening
  autocmd VimEnter * :call CheckDependencies()

